New Dawn - Seasonal Overview

2024-05-05

Introduction

Welcome to the New Dawn alliance overview!

This overview contains information on the entire alliance after every Star Expedition season. If for some reason you have any suggestions, comments or ideas, feel free to contact Danny:

  • Ingame: 104378119025
  • Discord: _.danny._.

After every Star Expedition season, every guild takes note of the following stats of each player:

  • Name
  • CCL - (Friends list lineup)
  • Star Expedition points
  • Number of A-tiers

These statistics are then used to display relevant information on the growth on all different levels.

Alliance

This section is devoted to displaying information on the entire Alliance level.

  • Currently, we have 3 different guilds in our alliance!
  • We have members in 36 different servers!

Power

The total CCL power of all players combined this season is 32 532 930 301!

The guilds are compared side-by-side in the figure below.

Next, we show a density plot covering the spread of the power per guild. The graph can be interpreted as follows:

  • The higher the graph goes, the more players are situated around that power level.
  • The more to the right the graph goes, the higher the power level, hence the stronger the player.

Having lots of strong players will result in a high graph far to the right and vice versa.

  • Per 1 point of CCL we scored 54 695.29 points in SE!
